Classification: Variety
Genre: Comedy | Music | Sketch/Improv
Status: New Series
Network: BBC THREE ( United Kingdom)

Live at the Electric features a collection of the best emerging talent currently getting the live comedy scene in a spin. The show also features stand-up from Russell Kane and a mixture of short films, quick-fire sketches and music.
